Ischys — third-party attributions
================================

Ischys itself is MIT-licensed (see LICENSE).

Exercise catalog and images
---------------------------

`frontend/assets/catalog/catalog.json` (the bundled on-device exercise catalog,
736 exercises) is derived from **free-exercise-db**:

    https://github.com/yuhonas/free-exercise-db

free-exercise-db is released into the public domain under **The Unlicense**.
No attribution is required; this notice is a courtesy.

Exercise images originate from the same project. The app runs entirely
on-device, so nothing about which exercises a user views ever leaves their
phone.

Previously
----------

Earlier revisions seeded the catalog from **wger** (https://wger.de). wger's
application is AGPL-3.0-or-later and its exercise data is Creative Commons
(CC-BY-SA). Redistributing that data inside an MIT repository would not have
carried the share-alike obligation, so it was removed in favour of a
public-domain source. No wger data remains in this repository.
